author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Tile shower floor protection tips…unfortunately I have to repair a cracked tile and I want to protect the new tile floor/grout. I’m using Stay Put Surface Protector because it’s padded and sticks to the tile but doesn’t leave behind sticky residue. This is also great for the curb and main bathroom floor. Many thanks to Trimaco for sponsoring this tutorial 🔥#tileprotection #bathroomremodel #homeremodel #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
